'''Shisho Shrine''' (四所神社) refers to various {{ill|Shrines|ja|神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in Japan that enshrine the {{ill|Shisho Myōjin|ja|四所明神|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or similar deities.
* {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Tsugaru)|ja|四所神社 (つがる市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tsugaru|ja|つがる市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Aomori Prefecture|ja|青森県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * Shisho Shrine (Ōtsuki) - Known as {{ill|Takaiwa Shisho Shrine|ja|高岩四所神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Located in {{ill|Ōtsuki|ja|大月市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Yamanashi Prefecture|ja|山形県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * Shisho Shrine (Tomisato) - Known as {{ill|Hiyoshikura Shisho Shrine|ja|日吉倉四所神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Located in {{ill|Tomisato|ja|富里市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Sanmu)|ja|四所神社 (山武市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in Sanmu City, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|四所神社 (豊岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Toyooka|ja|豊岡市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Totsukawa)|ja|四所神社 (十津川村)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Totsukawa|ja|十津川村|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Yoshino District|ja|吉野郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Tokushima)|ja|四所神社 (徳島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tokushima|ja|徳島市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Miyoshi, Yamashiro Town)|ja|四所神社 (三好市山城町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Yamashiro Town|ja|山城町大月|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Miyoshi|ja|三好市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Tokushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Shisho Shrine (Miyoshi, Nishi Iya)|ja|四所神社 (三好市西祖谷山村)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi Iya|ja|西祖谷山村後山|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Miyoshi City, Tokushima Prefecture.
